nodes.body: Nice! Would this allow us to get rid of `PSet` entirely?

My recollection from my experiments here is that I decided that `SmallSet` is unnecessary as you can just use sets with `[Small s]` typeclass assumptions and that `WFTree` was not worth the trouble compared to just accepting some code duplication between `PGame`/`PSet` and `IGame`/`ZFSet`.

pullRequest.title: feat: `SmallSet.{u} ` - sets with `u`-small models
